node.text:
@jeffmackdesigns is an entrepreneur that we truly admire here at @archdose. The main goal of his company is to create custom built furniture, with a combination of wood and epoxy finish, designed to last a life time! He built is empire from the ground up and has now a community of over 700,000 people.
Give us your thoughts on one of his personal favorites! 👇

WOOD: Maple
EPOXY: @ecopoxy FlowCast
PIGMENT: @ecopoxy Caviar
FORM MATERIAL: HDPE (High Density Polyethylene) and plywood with our Form Building Tape. We seal our forms with @akfixna Silicone.
SANDER/BUFFER: @gemindustriesinc 11” sander/buffer.
FINISH: @rubiomonocoatusa Pure 2C Oil.
-
Shop these supplies and more at www.JeffMackSupply.com.
-
Get a quote on a custom built table at www.JeffMackDesigns.com

node.text:
#archdose
Swipe Left! Send this to someone who needs to see this! 🤍

Casa GP

📍Mérida, Yucatán, México 🇲🇽
📐 @thisisown_ @felipe_caboclo_arquitetura
📷 @manolorsolis_fotografia

Located in the Yucatán Golf Club “Country Club” in the Yucatán peninsula.

The project was born from a collaboration between friendly firms that have a very similar way of projecting. With simple and clean geometry, a project is developed that revolves around inhabiting the exterior from any point of the house, with the terraces being a main point of the project. Transparency and privacy were the factors to consider when designing the project. With great views of the golf course and the magnificent surrounding trees existing in the environment.
